  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Diagnosis of congenital haemophilia A or B with inhibitors development against FVIII
             or FIX, respectively

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Prophylactic administration of any haemostatic drug within 3 last months prior to
             entering the trial.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
